@startuml
title 校园钓鱼防御平台 - 系统分层架构图

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam handwritten false

' 定义组件样式
skinparam component {
    BackgroundColor #E8F4FD
    BorderColor #2E7DDB
    ArrowColor #666666
}

' 表现层
component "表现层\n(Presentation Layer)" as Presentation {
    [React 18] as React
    [Ant Design 5] as Antd
    [React Router v6] as Router
    [ECharts 5] as Charts
    note right: UI交互、页面路由、\n数据可视化、用户交互处理
}

' 业务逻辑层
component "业务逻辑层\n(Business Layer)" as Business {
    [Django 4.2] as Django
    [DRF 3.14] as DRF
    [用户认证模块] as Auth
    [检测引擎模块] as Detection
    note right: 权限验证、业务规则处理、\n核心算法实现、数据校验
}

' 数据访问层
component "数据访问层\n(Data Access Layer)" as DataAccess {
    [Django ORM] as ORM
    [查询优化] as QueryOpt
    [事务管理] as Transaction
    note right: 封装数据库CRUD操作、\n提供数据持久化接口
}

' 基础设施层
component "基础设施层\n(Infrastructure Layer)" as Infrastructure {
    [SQLite 3] as SQLite
    [CORS中间件] as CORS
    [日志系统] as Logging
    [静态文件服务] as Static
    note right: 数据存储、跨域支持、\n日志记录、静态文件服务
}

' 关系连接
Presentation --> Business : HTTP/HTTPS + JSON\nRESTful API
Business --> DataAccess : Django ORM API
DataAccess --> Infrastructure : SQL + SQLite驱动

' 外部用户
actor 用户 as User

User --> Presentation : 浏览器访问

@enduml